column5: Hey guys,  I have got tired of east tribs for trout fishing and plan to do late season trout fishing @ either Meaford and Thornbury but wonder what the conditions are  Any updates are appreciated!
uhm .... no replies yet.  I assume that everyone is fishing at the moment, heehee
where are the "old joints" you are referring to?  Thanks
I believe he means his elbow, shoulder, knee and hip joints....not where he fishes.
